		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looking for some help compiling Nesicide2 on OSX 10.5x.
<br />
<br />I downloaded the .tar source file, but after that I'm at a loss.  I've been messing with it off and on all day, but other than firing up terminal and making a new directory I'm not sure where to start.  I haven't been able to find much documentation either.
<br />
<br />I'm currently hanging out in the nesicide IRC, but nobody is around.
<br />
<br />Any help would be greatly appreciated.
<br />
<br />Thanks,
<br />Mattdc.

		

