	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />/me goes to the irc channel to help out
<br />
<br />Edit: these should be the steps needed:
<br />
<br />download git (needed to be able to download the latest revision of the source code)
<br />download <a href="http://get.qt.nokia.com/qtsdk/qt-sdk-mac-opensource-2010.02.dmg" class="postlink">Qt-dev kit/libs</a> (needed for gui, project files etc)
<br />download <a href="http://www.libsdl.org/release/SDL-1.2.14.dmg" class="postlink">sdl frameworks</a> (needed for audio, might be installed with the developer tools on 10.5 though)
<br />
<br />download the nesicide2 source code via git:
<br />git clone <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="git://gitorious.org/nesicide/nesicide2-master.git">git://gitorious.org/nesicide/nesicide2-master.git</a><!-- m --> path/to/nesicide2
<br />
<br />open up Qt Creator from /Developer/Applications/Qt/
<br />open up the nesicide project
<br />set build configuration to "release" in the build menu
<br />build the project (command + b)
<br />run the project (command + r)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
